rows.label: qst202410_0010
rows.name: Well, that's got them in a proper tizzy!

rows.label: qst202410_0020
rows.name: They are most delight by songstress song, craa!

rows.label: qst202410_0030
rows.name:
We mek Nopon new kountess!
That's why Tirkin excites!

rows.label: qst202410_0040
rows.name: And you're OK with that...?

rows.label: qst202410_0050
rows.name:
Huh, and we thought you might have wanted your
real countess back.

rows.label: qst202410_0060
rows.name: Y-you find real kountess?! Craaa!

rows.label: qst202410_0070
rows.name: Much thanks, heroes! You save our kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0080
rows.name:
I dunno if we "saved" her as such. She did look
like she'd been enjoying herself.

rows.label: qst202410_0090
rows.name: She definitely took a bit of persuading.

rows.label: qst202410_0100
rows.name: We most grateful.

rows.label: qst202410_0110
rows.name: Kome! We celebrate return of kountess together!

rows.label: qst202410_0120
rows.name: You mean, we get to eat free tasties?!

rows.label: qst202410_0130
rows.name:
I wonder if they have my favorite,
Juicy Samod?

rows.label: qst202410_0140
rows.name:
What? I don't think that's
your favorite, Ibuki.

rows.label: qst202410_0150
rows.name:
Oh, yeah, silly me, I meant
Cream Orange Paratha.

rows.label: qst202410_0160
rows.name: That's MY favorite, you twit!

rows.label: qst202410_0170
rows.name: ...Anyway, I see no reason to decline. Shall we?

rows.label: qst202410_0180
rows.name: Uhh... Have you guys seen Ibuki?

rows.label: qst202410_0190
rows.name: Mm? She was right next to you until a moment ago.

rows.label: qst202410_0200
rows.name: Craaa! The moment you are all waiting! Return of kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0210
rows.name: Behold! True Tirkin kountess is heres!

rows.label: qst202410_0220
rows.name: What the-?!

rows.label: qst202410_0230
rows.name: Kountess safe!

rows.label: qst202410_0240
rows.name: Happy dance! Happy dance!

rows.label: qst202410_0250
rows.name: What does she think she's playing at?!

rows.label: qst202410_0260
rows.name: Hey! Ibuki! You're not their countess, remember!

rows.label: qst202410_0270
rows.name: Heya, folks! I'm Ibuki! Tee-hee!

rows.label: qst202410_0280
rows.name: Oooooohhh!!!

rows.label: qst202410_0290
rows.name: She not your kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0300
rows.name: I is only kountess Tirkin is needing!

rows.label: qst202410_0310
rows.name: Kountess?!

rows.label: qst202410_0320
rows.name: Two kountess?! But which right one kountess?!

rows.label: qst202410_0330
rows.name: Is thats kountess?!

rows.label: qst202410_0340
rows.name: No! Small one kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0350
rows.name: Double kountess?

rows.label: qst202410_0360
rows.name: Multikountess!!!

rows.label: qst202410_0370
rows.name: Oh, come on. It's clearly the one on the right!

rows.label: qst202410_0380
rows.name: SILENCE!!!

rows.label: qst202410_0390
rows.name: We have kountess pair!

rows.label: qst202410_0400
rows.name: Oooooohhh!!!

rows.label: qst202410_0410
rows.name: Double sovereign! So happies!

rows.label: qst202410_0420
rows.name: Happy happy!

rows.label: qst202410_0430
rows.name: Noes! I am kountess! Only one kountess!

rows.label: qst202410_0440
rows.name: Rejoice!

rows.label: qst202410_0450
rows.name:
So many kountess! Brink peace
to all Tirkin!

rows.label: qst202410_0460
rows.name: Tirkin really are the best!

rows.label: qst202410_0470
rows.name: Whooooooa!!!

rows.label: qst202410_0480
rows.name: Tirkin seem super-duper excited...

rows.label: qst202410_0490
rows.name: It would be a tall order trying to rein them in now.

rows.label: qst202410_0500
rows.name: Ah, now me remember...

rows.label: qst202410_0510
rows.name:
Tirkin all complete birdbrain! It easies for Tirkin
to forget kountess even!

rows.label: qst202410_0520
rows.name: That why I did runned away!

rows.label: qst202410_0530
rows.name: There, there. It'll all be fine. It'll be fine!

rows.label: qst202410_0540
rows.name:
What are friends for? I'll clear things up for you
AND I'll explain to them what happened.

rows.label: qst202410_0550
rows.name: Flinch... Oh, Flinch! Much thank, Flinch!

rows.label: qst202410_0560
rows.name: It's Ibuki, not Flinch! But thanks, Omelette.

rows.label: qst202410_0570
rows.name: Wrong! My name is Omulette! No to forget!

rows.label: qst202410_0580
rows.name: *bumbling* Darn, those Tirkin names sure are hard...

rows.label: qst202410_0590
rows.name:
Never mind. I won't forget it now.
Promise you that, Amulet!

rows.label: qst202410_0600
rows.name:
Omulette! I telling you, Flench, my name
is Omulette!

rows.label: qst202410_0610
rows.name:
F-IN-CH, not Flench! Come on, it's not that hard!
Not like Emulotte!

rows.label: qst202410_0620
rows.name:
Omulette! Why you always get
wrong, Fronch!

rows.label: qst202410_0630
rows.name: Oooooohhh!!!

rows.label: qst202410_0640
rows.name: Look at those stooges. This is getting ridiculous...

rows.label: qst202410_0650
rows.name:
Can't see this ending any time soon. They don't
seem to know how to deliver a proper punchline...
